    {
      "chinese": "其次，要栽培阿美族最具原民風味的傳統作物。所有銷售的物品一定要註明產地的部落名稱，建立屬於自己的品牌，以提升知名度。最好是附加部落的緣由，以祖先的故事或傳說為依據，提高部落休閒農場的知名度。",
      "ab": "Do^do^ sato, mipaloma^ to kahirahira a sinafel no Pangcah. Tokien a mipangangan a maemin ko nipacakayan to kalomaamaan, ta matenak a macakat ko sakacinganganaw, mangalef ano pacipingen ko kongko^ no niyaro’ ato no to’as a mirayray, o mamacakat ko nikacingangan to pihololan a omah i niyaro’.",
